ActCanada Marine Act
SubjectRemoval of provincial directors of the Hamilton and Oshawa Port Authority - David Bradley and Patricia Perkins
PrecisOrder approving the REMOVAL of DAVID BRADLEY as the director of the Hamilton Port Authority and PARTICIA PERKINS as the director of the Oshawa Port Authority, who were appointed by the Province of Ontario, to ensure that membership of the Hamilton-Oshawa Port Authority's Board of Directors is consistent with the provisions of the Canada Marine Act, effective June 17, 2019.
